  66:     -	00E4          	RDTKDLY		EQU	RDTRK+100B	;WRITE TRACK COMMAND with 15ms settling delay (179x/1773: 30ms if 1MHz)
  67:     -	00F4          	WRTKDLY		EQU	WRTRK+100B	;READ TRACK COMMAND with 15ms settling delay (179x/1773: 30ms if 1MHz)
